01:02:44,720 --> 01:02:47,440
And then he says, I bought him a pound of nuts.

683
01:02:47,441 --> 01:02:48,880
And now, pay attention.

684
01:02:48,880 --> 01:02:51,761
Everything that happens is absolutely amazing.

685
01:02:52,161 --> 01:02:54,640
For no one had ever bought him a pound of nuts before.

686
01:02:54,641 --> 01:02:58,720
