01:09:55,361 --> 01:09:59,601
It's not causal in the physics and chemistry and neural way.

761
01:09:59,760 --> 01:10:12,400
That is, he doesn't have a theory, and he doesn't need one, and he probably doesn't think there is one, of how these existential experiences happen on the level of the way the brain works and so forth.

762
01:10:12,401 --> 01:10:16,880
He wants a description that captures the whole meaning of it.

763
01:10:16,880 --> 01:10:28,400
