764
01:10:28,720 --> 01:10:40,960
What's important is that this, you have to understand the meaning of how it is that holding up the baby to the icon or giving the pound of nuts can influence somebody all their lives.

765
01:10:42,241 --> 01:10:45,440
It doesn't matter whether you have a neuron story about it.

